#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/gizmos.rst:69
msgid ""
"You can use the widget by dragging one of the three colored axes with :kbd:"
"`LMB`. The transformation will be locked to the clicked axis."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过 :kbd:`LMB` 拖动三个颜色轴中的一个来使用小部件。变换将被锁定到点击的"
"轴向。"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/gizmos.rst:72
msgid ""
"Dragging the small white circle allows free transformation. In case of the "
"rotation gizmo this starts a :ref:`trackball rotation <view3d-transform-"
"trackball>`. The rotation gizmo contains another big outer white circle to "
"activate free transformation."
msgstr ""
"拖动中心的小白圈是自由变换。在旋转Gizmo的情况下这将启动 :ref:`轨迹球旋转 "
"<view3d-transform-trackball>` 。旋转Gizmo包含另一个大的外部白色圆圈以激活自由"
"变换。"

#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/gizmos.rst:76
msgid "Releasing the mouse confirms the operation (*confirm on release*)."
msgstr "释放鼠标确认操作(*确认释放*)。"

