#: ../../manual/scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/gizmos.rst:85
msgid ""
"Holding down :kbd:`Shift` *after* you :kbd:`LMB` the gizmo handle will "
"constrain the action to smaller increments. Holding down :kbd:`Shift` *before* "
"you :kbd:`LMB` click on one of the handles will cause the gizmo action to be "
"performed relative to the other two axes. See :ref:`view3d-transform-plane-"
"lock`."
msgstr ""
"当你点击 :kbd:`LMB` *之后* 按住 :kbd:`Shift` 不放的话Gizmo控制柄将以更精细的增"
"量运动。当你点击 :kbd:`LMB` *之前* 按住 :kbd:`Shift` 不放的话，控制柄将使得Gizmo"
"操作表现为只在另外两个轴向运动。参见 :ref:`view3d-transform-plane-lock` 。"

